column5: I will represent the Western folk with a picture posted on another website. I cant believe deer get this big......I wonder if they eat people?
I frequent OTB and they have a great group of guys over there.....all you hunters should check it out
Even if it was spam...he's right it's good spam lol
Cripes thats a huge Buck  I don't know about eating other people...but other deer for sure!
